cff-version: 1.2.0
message: "If you use PAK, please cite the paper and the dataset."
title: "PAK: A Survey-Grounded Synthetic Persona Dataset of the Korean Cultural Arts Workforce"
abstract: >-
  PAK (Persona Arts Korea) is a synthetic persona dataset of the Korean
  cultural arts workforce, grounded cell-by-cell in the 2024 Survey of Korean
  Artists via per-field iterative proportional fitting, with a co-released
  human-versus-model-panel evaluation layer (PAK-1K-eval).
type: dataset
authors:
